CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 25, 1959, pg. 13 reads: "County Court Staff - Front to rear: Ethel T. Posey clerk; Melvin Mrdjenovich, clerk, and Pauline S. Brvenik, utility clerk."
TitMainTitle: Clerks Ethel T. Posey, Melvin Mrdjenovich, and Pauline S. Brvenik, seated in office with large ledgers, in Allegheny County Courts office, man and woman in background on right
